    "stdyInfo": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Les objectifs de ce projet intitulé « Presaje » étaient de connaitre l’état et les attitudes de santé des jeunes suivis en Missions locales et de comprendre leurs comportements de recours (ou de non recours) afin d’améliorer leur accès aux soins et évaluer l’impact éventuel sur leur insertion socio-professionnelle."
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "The objectives of this project, titled \"Presaje\", were to find out the health conditions and attitudes toward health of youths monitored in local Missions and to understand their health care use (or non-use) behaviours in order to improve their access to care and to evaluate any impact on their social integration and job placement."
        }
      ],
